%% Sequence Diagram — Approve Pending Event

sequenceDiagram
    actor Approver
    participant UI as Events Page
    participant API as PATCH /events/id/approve
    participant Auth as NextAuth Session
    participant Svc as event-review.ts
    participant CD as conflict.ts
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Org as Organiser Inbox

    Approver->>UI: Click Approve
    UI->>API: PATCH request + cookie
    API->>Auth: Verify session & role
    Auth-->>API: APPROVER confirmed
    API->>Svc: approvePendingEvent()
    Svc->>DB: Load event (PENDING)
    Svc->>CD: detectVenueConflict()
    CD->>DB: Query overlapping events
    DB-->>CD: Result
  alt Conflict exists
        CD-->>Svc: conflicting event
        Svc-->>API: CONFLICT error
        API-->>UI: 409 response
    else No conflict
        Svc->>DB: Update status APPROVED
        Svc->>DB: Create notification
        Svc->>DB: Resolve ConflictLog rows
        Svc-->>API: Success
        API-->>UI: 200 OK
        DB-->>Org: EVENT_APPROVED notification
    end
